      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEROCCA BERNIE (11) comes through the Gold Chalice series where he was runner-up in his heat before coming from this row and finishing just over 10m off the winner in the Group 2 final. Owns a strong record at this circuit and distance and will enjoy the class drop. COWBOY CULTURE (6) showed good improvement when he finished third last start, beaten 2.5 metres at this circuit and distance. Gets the same draw but should be approaching peak fitness fourth up. Capable of playing a major role. AURORA MIGHTY ROB (9) beat a handy one in a last-start win by a nose at this circuit and distance and draws for a trail. ENJABONARLO (10) went to the paddock off back-to-back wins. Hasn't raced since October but has trialled nicely twice recently so keep safe.",
